description:
The rapid growth of the Coronavirus (COVID-19) including its recent entrance into America  is creating fear and panic worldwide. If this virus hits your neighborhood, or if you should catch it while traveling, what should you do? How can you protect yourself and your loved ones? In this new White Horse Media video, Steve Wohlberg interviews Dr. Ronald Fleck who offers practical steps to avoid being another corona-casualty.
